1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:35,330 --> 00:01:38,950
[Lost Identity]

3
00:01:42,770 --> 00:01:45,560
[Episode 32]

4
00:01:46,630 --> 00:01:48,400
I've thought it over and over.

5
00:01:48,509 --> 00:01:50,910
I feel like I can only come to you about this.

6
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,360
How about it?

7
00:02:01,630 --> 00:02:02,960
This matter is not easy.

8
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,270
If it were

9
00:02:04,950 --> 00:02:06,880
just kidnapping someone,  it would be doable.

10
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:08,810
But his identity is too sensitive.

11
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,440
So many people are watching.

12
00:02:10,750 --> 00:02:12,950
And I need to get information out of him.

13
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,610
That's not easy.

14
00:02:14,620 --> 00:02:15,590
I know it's difficult.

15
00:02:15,590 --> 00:02:17,990
If it were easy, I wouldn't have come to you.

16
00:02:19,829 --> 00:02:20,840
Let me tell you,

17
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,310
if this goes

18
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:24,230
even slightly wrong,

19
00:02:24,340 --> 00:02:26,040
it will bring trouble upon us.

20
00:02:26,310 --> 00:02:27,820
At this critical moment,

21
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:30,240
don't do anything that complicates things further.

22
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,220
If one link is disrupted,

23
00:02:31,220 --> 00:02:34,070
the whole chain will fall apart. Do you understand?

24
00:02:34,070 --> 00:02:35,810
Are you bargaining with me?

25
00:02:35,950 --> 00:02:37,160
Not bargaining.

26
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,810
It's just really hard to do.

27
00:02:43,820 --> 00:02:46,020
I can help you find Lu Ziming and his men.

28
00:02:48,490 --> 00:02:50,000
You have news of Lu Ziming?

29
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,390
My brother has connections in Chongqing.

30
00:02:53,390 --> 00:02:55,320
You shouldn't underestimate him.

31
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:57,800
Your brother is so capable.

32
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,040
Why don't you ask him to handle it?

33
00:02:59,040 --> 00:02:59,790
Well.

34
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:02,400
What leverage do they have over you?

35
00:03:07,470 --> 00:03:09,800
Alright, I won't hide it from you anymore.

36
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:11,310
Back then, when we attacked

37
00:03:11,310 --> 00:03:12,640
Ohashi in Hongkou Park,

38
00:03:13,010 --> 00:03:15,010
Zheng Bangyao and I were both there.

39
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:17,960
The purpose was to save those students.

40
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:21,280
Were you there too?

41
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:23,230
Why do you look familiar?

42
00:03:24,950 --> 00:03:26,120
Don't worry about me.

43
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,579
Just tell me your problem.

44
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:32,240
Now, Zeng Jiwu

45
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:33,950
is making a big fuss

46
00:03:34,030 --> 00:03:36,030
to bring Zheng Bangyao to Chongqing

47
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:38,410
just to smear me.

48
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,030
You should know better than I do

49
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:41,829
what kind of person Zeng Jiwu is.

50
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,290
If you don't help me,

51
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:51,160
I'm

52
00:03:52,070 --> 00:03:53,680
finished.

53
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:04,400
I'll think of a way.

54
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,150
This must

55
00:04:06,510 --> 00:04:07,830
not go wrong.

56
00:04:09,030 --> 00:04:09,910
Otherwise,

57
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,550
we'll both be done for.

58
00:04:18,410 --> 00:04:19,610
Thank you in advance.

59
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:26,670
[Zhicheng Hotel]

60
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:29,300
We have single rooms and suites here.

61
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,560
Take care.

62
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:31,840
Come again next time.

63
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,440
By the way, at the end of the corridor on the second floor,

64
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:35,320
on the right hand...

65
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:36,720
Room 405, Mr. Zheng.

66
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:38,480
Are you extending your stay?

67
00:04:39,030 --> 00:04:39,990
Mr. Zheng?

68
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:42,560
We'll see.

69
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:43,440
Thank you.

70
00:04:44,190 --> 00:04:45,150
Take care.

71
00:04:50,770 --> 00:04:53,880
[Zhicheng Hotel]

72
00:05:03,130 --> 00:05:04,670
Why was that man wearing a mask just now?

73
00:05:04,670 --> 00:05:06,000
He was being secretive.

74
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:10,120
He must be afraid of being recognized.

75
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,230
There are

76
00:05:11,330 --> 00:05:14,190
plenty of people coming to Chongqing to smuggle

77
00:05:14,230 --> 00:05:15,250
and inform these days.

78
00:05:15,250 --> 00:05:17,510
Let's not get involved. Get back to work.

79
00:06:01,270 --> 00:06:02,530
Are you Zheng Bangyao?

80
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:04,740
Who are you?

81
00:06:05,230 --> 00:06:06,750
I’m Ou Xiao'an from NBIS's

82
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,520
Operations Department.

83
00:06:11,110 --> 00:06:12,590
I saw you wet your pants

84
00:06:12,590 --> 00:06:14,920
on Scott Road before. You don't remember?

85
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:19,800
What should I say about you?

86
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:21,960
These are just a bunch of kids.

87
00:06:22,340 --> 00:06:24,470
If they knew anything, they would have told you already.

88
00:06:24,470 --> 00:06:26,040
Do you have to resort to such methods?

89
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,240
Right, Captain Zeng?

90
00:06:28,460 --> 00:06:29,650
Nonsense.

91
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,240
Remember now?

92
00:06:36,260 --> 00:06:37,140
Captain Ou.

93
00:06:38,260 --> 00:06:40,270
Why... Why are you here?

94
00:06:40,550 --> 00:06:43,060
The station sent me to escort you.

95
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:45,330
They're afraid you might be in danger.

96
00:06:48,540 --> 00:06:49,300
But

97
00:06:49,610 --> 00:06:51,480
didn’t they say to meet

98
00:06:51,780 --> 00:06:53,580
at the mass grave outside the east of the city at 3 p.m.?

99
00:06:53,580 --> 00:06:54,340
Yes.

100
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,440
But there are a lot of bandits

101
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,880
on this road.

102
00:06:58,290 --> 00:07:00,080
The station is afraid you might encounter trouble.

103
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:02,190
So they specifically instructed me to protect you.

104
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:03,120
But...

105
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:05,210
Captain Zeng specifically told me

106
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,950
to drive myself.

107
00:07:08,060 --> 00:07:10,310
Captain Zeng is also my colleague now.

108
00:07:10,750 --> 00:07:13,050
Captain Zeng is not convenient to show his face.

109
00:07:13,050 --> 00:07:15,180
Moreover, the station's superiors

110
00:07:15,220 --> 00:07:16,830
value you highly.

111
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:19,160
We can’t let anything happen to you.

112
00:07:19,230 --> 00:07:20,430
So they sent me.

113
00:07:25,370 --> 00:07:26,570
It's almost time.

114
00:07:27,550 --> 00:07:28,360
I’ll drive.

115
00:07:28,550 --> 00:07:29,610
You sit in the back.

116
00:08:00,350 --> 00:08:01,280
Ma'am.

117
00:08:02,430 --> 00:08:03,840
Are you worried

118
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,960
that Miss Qin's plan might have problems?

119
00:08:06,990 --> 00:08:09,910
Ou Xiao'an's identity hasn't been fully confirmed.

120
00:08:09,910 --> 00:08:11,550
Involving him at this point

121
00:08:12,660 --> 00:08:14,060
is still very risky.

122
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:18,010
Miss Qin won’t let him

123
00:08:18,030 --> 00:08:19,360
know too much.

124
00:08:20,310 --> 00:08:21,150
And

125
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:24,160
her plan is very thorough.

126
00:08:24,350 --> 00:08:25,550
As long as Ou Xiao'an

127
00:08:26,010 --> 00:08:28,810
brings Zheng Bangyao to our designated location,

128
00:08:29,110 --> 00:08:30,390
after he leaves,

129
00:08:31,050 --> 00:08:33,120
we'll pick up the person separately.

130
00:08:33,820 --> 00:08:35,730
We won't let them meet each other.

131
00:08:37,570 --> 00:08:39,570
Is there anything foolproof

132
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,679
when it involves people?

133
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:23,640
Captain Ou.

134
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:26,510
When did you join NBIS?

135
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:30,590
I’ve always been with NBIS.

136
00:09:31,340 --> 00:09:32,800
That time on Scott Road...

137
00:09:37,270 --> 00:09:39,030
Understood.

138
00:09:41,680 --> 00:09:45,220
Has Captain Zeng joined your Operations Department too?

139
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:46,880
Captain Zeng?

140
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,190
Captain Zeng

141
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:52,500
recently joined NBIS.

142
00:09:54,580 --> 00:09:55,660
In that case,

143
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:57,640
you are his senior.

144
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,520
I heard that you’re here

145
00:10:03,980 --> 00:10:05,900
to report a communist, right?

146
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:10,090
Is your information accurate?

147
00:10:10,660 --> 00:10:12,190
This is Chongqing Station.

148
00:10:12,230 --> 00:10:13,680
If your information

149
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:15,030
is faulty,

150
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:18,220
no one can guarantee you’ll leave alive.

151
00:10:18,470 --> 00:10:19,150
Accurate.

152
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,450
Definitely accurate.

153
00:10:20,450 --> 00:10:22,070
Qin Moqing saved me back then.

154
00:10:22,070 --> 00:10:23,190
And I saw her

155
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,670
with Ye Xuanmin.

156
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:30,280
Why didn’t you report this

157
00:10:31,130 --> 00:10:32,690
back on Scott Road?

158
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:38,650
I didn’t know

159
00:10:39,230 --> 00:10:40,960
who she was back then.

160
00:10:41,410 --> 00:10:42,850
Besides, she saved me.

161
00:10:43,170 --> 00:10:45,110
It was just a few days ago

162
00:10:45,390 --> 00:10:47,190
that Captain Zeng sent me a photo

163
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,250
to identify her.

164
00:10:48,340 --> 00:10:49,180
He also said

165
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:51,310
there would be a reward of ten gold bars

166
00:10:51,310 --> 00:10:53,170
for significant contributions.

167
00:10:54,110 --> 00:10:55,040
That's why

168
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:57,520
I came forward.

169
00:10:57,910 --> 00:11:00,570
Captain Zeng promised to give you ten gold bars?

170
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:03,500
Besides Captain Zeng,

171
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:05,470
did you tell anyone else about this matter?

172
00:11:05,470 --> 00:11:07,520
No, I haven’t told anyone.

173
00:11:08,110 --> 00:11:09,800
Captain Zeng specifically instructed me

174
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:11,110
not to mention it to anyone

175
00:11:11,110 --> 00:11:13,550
until I arrived in Chongqing.

176
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,000
Of course.

177
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:18,040
You're not an outsider.

178
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:21,600
That's good.

179
00:12:22,860 --> 00:12:24,140
It's been two hours.

180
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:34,270
Go back to the station.

181
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:34,950
Yes.

182
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,200
Captain Ou.

183
00:13:03,970 --> 00:13:06,230
This isn’t the way to the east of the city.

184
00:13:06,330 --> 00:13:07,660
Where are you taking me?

185
00:13:08,020 --> 00:13:10,170
The station is afraid of leaks,

186
00:13:10,300 --> 00:13:12,350
which could compromise your safety.

187
00:13:12,350 --> 00:13:13,440
So they instructed me

188
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:15,080
to take you to our safe house.

189
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,380
Safe house?

190
00:13:16,710 --> 00:13:17,950
Safe house.

191
00:13:19,020 --> 00:13:20,180
You’re not from NBIS.

192
00:13:20,180 --> 00:13:21,730
You’re with Qin Moqing.

193
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:23,910
Did she send you to kill me?

194
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:25,200
Calm down.

195
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:27,560
I’m here to ensure your safety. Don't worry.

196
00:13:27,560 --> 00:13:29,990
I don’t believe you unless you stop the car right now.

197
00:13:29,990 --> 00:13:32,410
Otherwise, we die together.

198
00:13:32,710 --> 00:13:33,550
Stop the car!

199
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:35,670
Stop the car!

200
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:47,760
Where is he?

201
00:13:47,900 --> 00:13:49,800
Impossible.

202
00:13:49,980 --> 00:13:52,640
It was supposed to be 3 p.m.

203
00:13:52,770 --> 00:13:55,300
at the mass grave outside the east of the city.

204
00:13:55,970 --> 00:13:57,440
Captain, I...

205
00:13:58,190 --> 00:14:01,190
Could it be that the person picking him up had an issue?

206
00:14:01,740 --> 00:14:03,540
I personally went to pick him up.

207
00:14:04,230 --> 00:14:06,840
I waited at the mass grave for two hours.

208
00:14:06,860 --> 00:14:08,500
Was there any Buick?

209
00:14:08,690 --> 00:14:11,420
I only saw a bull cart carrying manure.

210
00:14:11,510 --> 00:14:12,350
I... I’ll check.

211
00:14:12,350 --> 00:14:13,150
I’ll check.

212
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,600
Section Chief Qin, busy?

213
00:14:45,950 --> 00:14:46,960
Captain Zeng.

214
00:14:47,510 --> 00:14:48,710
Anything important?

215
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:49,640
Nothing.

216
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:51,010
I just remembered

217
00:14:51,040 --> 00:14:52,720
your advice.

218
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:56,030
I want to deepen

219
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,770
my impression with Mr. Qin.

220
00:14:57,880 --> 00:14:59,430
You should have said earlier.

221
00:14:59,430 --> 00:15:00,950
My brother is out of town.

222
00:15:01,490 --> 00:15:02,410
Wait a few days.

223
00:15:03,190 --> 00:15:03,920
It's okay.

224
00:15:04,460 --> 00:15:06,260
No rush. A couple of days is fine.

225
00:15:11,020 --> 00:15:12,570
So, Captain Zeng,

226
00:15:12,780 --> 00:15:14,580
are you here to inspect my work?

227
00:15:15,920 --> 00:15:16,900
I wouldn't dare.

228
00:15:16,980 --> 00:15:17,960
-Come on.
-That’s not necessary.

229
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:18,680
Please.

230
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:21,430
Not at all.

231
00:15:21,640 --> 00:15:23,400
Don’t, Captain Zeng.

232
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:25,400
Given your current status

233
00:15:25,400 --> 00:15:27,150
with Captain Wei,

234
00:15:27,150 --> 00:15:29,470
nothing you do is excessive. Please.

235
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:31,390
Section Chief Qin,

236
00:15:31,590 --> 00:15:33,360
don't make fun of me.

237
00:15:42,700 --> 00:15:44,160
Where’s Section Chief Ou?

238
00:15:44,170 --> 00:15:45,770
I haven’t seen him all day.

239
00:15:47,640 --> 00:15:48,350
Our Operations Department

240
00:15:48,350 --> 00:15:49,870
has its own rules.

241
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:51,670
We can't ask about others' tasks.

242
00:15:51,670 --> 00:15:52,880
Why? Looking for him?

243
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:54,600
I’ll let him know when he returns.

244
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:56,120
No, no, it’s fine.

245
00:16:07,620 --> 00:16:10,950
[Zhicheng Hotel]

246
00:16:18,630 --> 00:16:20,000
Someone called you.

247
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:21,080
Who?

248
00:16:21,150 --> 00:16:22,810
He said his last name is Zheng.

249
00:16:25,950 --> 00:16:27,010
Section Chief Qin.

250
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:28,890
I won't bother you anymore.

251
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:42,830
Is it Zheng Bangyao?

252
00:16:44,350 --> 00:16:45,140
Speak.

253
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:48,010
Speak, Zheng Bangyao.

254
00:16:52,790 --> 00:16:53,800
Hello.

255
00:16:56,430 --> 00:16:57,590
I didn’t make the call.

256
00:16:57,590 --> 00:16:58,760
Mr. Zheng did.

257
00:16:58,840 --> 00:16:59,550
Where is he?

258
00:17:00,050 --> 00:17:01,980
He left.

259
00:17:02,710 --> 00:17:04,170
Catch up with him quickly.

260
00:17:04,270 --> 00:17:05,240
Alright.

261
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:09,329
Mr. Zheng.

262
00:17:09,430 --> 00:17:12,589
Mr. Zheng.

263
00:17:18,740 --> 00:17:20,329
[Zhicheng Hotel]

264
00:17:23,430 --> 00:17:25,970
Sir, the car has gone far. I didn't catch up.

265
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:27,660
But he left something for you.

266
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:28,750
When will you come to get it?

267
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:29,760
What is it?

268
00:17:29,830 --> 00:17:30,950
A briefcase.

269
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:34,140
Mr. Zheng, you’re back. I’ll get the key for you.

270
00:17:34,670 --> 00:17:36,040
I’m not extending my stay tonight.

271
00:17:36,040 --> 00:17:36,680
Please deliver this

272
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:38,530
to Mr. Zeng Jiwu.

273
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:39,600
Tell him

274
00:17:39,670 --> 00:17:40,590
I’m out.

275
00:17:41,570 --> 00:17:42,370
Okay.

276
00:17:47,660 --> 00:17:49,700
He called and left.

277
00:17:50,090 --> 00:17:51,010
Open it.

278
00:17:52,670 --> 00:17:53,810
Open it!

279
00:17:53,830 --> 00:17:55,300
Okay, wait a moment.

280
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:18,470
Mr. Zeng, right?

281
00:18:21,510 --> 00:18:23,630
This is what Mr. Zheng left for you.

282
00:18:28,950 --> 00:18:30,330
What else did he say?

283
00:18:31,090 --> 00:18:33,920
He asked me to tell Zeng Jiwu that he would quit.

284
00:18:36,590 --> 00:18:37,620
Take care.

285
00:18:42,950 --> 00:18:45,300
What was he wearing? What was he driving?

286
00:18:47,030 --> 00:18:50,290
He was wearing a black striped coat.

287
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:52,130
