[Li Shaotang and Feng Jingxian's Wedding Notice]

580
00:36:31,520 --> 00:36:32,440
Mr. Wen.

581
00:36:33,040 --> 00:36:33,640
Xiao'an.

582
00:36:33,680 --> 00:36:34,560
Come here.

583
00:36:35,470 --> 00:36:36,310
Sit.

584
00:36:46,110 --> 00:36:46,800
Here.

585
00:36:47,400 --> 00:36:48,200
Have some tea.

586
00:36:49,390 --> 00:36:50,520
Thank you, Captain.

587
00:36:53,300 --> 00:36:55,660
Been good lately?

588
00:36:56,280 --> 00:36:57,630
Always been good.

589
00:37:03,750 --> 00:37:04,750
Here's the thing.

590
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:06,530
A few days ago,

591
00:37:06,550 --> 00:37:08,550
we were busy at the station.

592
00:37:08,760 --> 00:37:09,890
These days

593
00:37:09,990 --> 00:37:11,590
there hasn’t been much to do.

594
00:37:11,710 --> 00:37:13,520
You can

595
00:37:14,180 --> 00:37:15,330
take a few days off.

596
00:37:19,340 --> 00:37:20,930
The station was busy.

597
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:22,920
It was not just me.

598
00:37:23,310 --> 00:37:24,460
I don't need to rest.

599
00:37:33,160 --> 00:37:35,690
Mr. Wen, if there’s something, just say it.

600
00:37:37,750 --> 00:37:39,850
Have you seen Li Shaotang today?

601
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:42,500
No.

602
00:37:42,850 --> 00:37:44,880
But a while ago, I went to his air raid shelter.

603
00:37:44,880 --> 00:37:46,130
Captain Wei and I...

604
00:37:46,150 --> 00:37:47,020
Xiao'an.

605
00:37:48,910 --> 00:37:50,440
I'll emphasize it again.

606
00:37:51,010 --> 00:37:52,420
Don’t interfere in

607
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:54,730
Li Shaotang’s affairs.

608
00:37:56,850 --> 00:37:58,570
Don't get in my way.

609
00:38:02,080 --> 00:38:03,130
You see.

610
00:38:03,350 --> 00:38:04,950
Those are the inner demons.

611
00:38:05,230 --> 00:38:06,340
They will blind you

612
00:38:06,390 --> 00:38:08,190
to the truth.

613
00:38:14,650 --> 00:38:17,250
[Li Shaotang and Feng Jingxian's Wedding Notice]

614
00:38:19,150 --> 00:38:19,920
Understood.

615
00:38:21,500 --> 00:38:23,740
Have a good rest for a few days.

616
00:38:25,550 --> 00:38:26,390
Sure.

617
00:38:27,810 --> 00:38:29,280
[Qin Moqing]

618
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:30,660
[on the 14th day of the eighth lunar month]

619
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:30,660
[We sincerely invite you to attend the wedding of our daughter Jingxian and Mr. Li Shaotang]

620
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:41,320
What is it?

621
00:38:43,160 --> 00:38:44,110
I've decided

622
00:38:44,550 --> 00:38:47,550
to set the action on the 14th of the eighth lunar month.

623
00:38:50,910 --> 00:38:52,710
[on the 14th day of the eighth lunar month]

624
00:38:50,910 --> 00:38:52,710
[We sincerely invite you to attend the wedding of our daughter Jingxian and Mr. Li Shaotang]

625
00:38:54,400 --> 00:38:55,600
You did it on purpose?

626
00:38:57,430 --> 00:38:58,310
I know.

627
00:38:58,850 --> 00:39:00,490
It’s normal for me

628
00:39:01,020 --> 00:39:02,160
not to go to this wedding.

629
00:39:02,160 --> 00:39:03,760
It would be strange if I went.

630
00:39:06,540 --> 00:39:07,720
Can you handle it alone?

631
00:39:07,720 --> 00:39:09,310
That day is the only chance.

632
00:39:09,530 --> 00:39:10,460
Otherwise,

633
00:39:10,790 --> 00:39:12,850
there won’t be another opportunity.

634
00:39:16,810 --> 00:39:17,850
Just be aware.

635
00:39:32,780 --> 00:39:33,640
Director Shen.

636
00:39:33,940 --> 00:39:35,190
Captain Wei of Chongqing Station

637
00:39:35,190 --> 00:39:36,640
has also handed over Li Manqiu.

638
00:39:36,640 --> 00:39:38,300
I brought him here yesterday.

639
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:43,290
As the Kuomintang-Communist peace talks approach,

640
00:39:43,470 --> 00:39:46,270
Ye Xuanmin's movements are extremely sensitive.

641
00:39:47,270 --> 00:39:49,490
We must ensure that no information leaks out.

642
00:39:49,490 --> 00:39:50,260
Got it.

643
00:39:53,550 --> 00:39:57,000
[Jiangjin]

644
00:40:08,030 --> 00:40:08,890
Director Shen.

645
00:40:09,580 --> 00:40:10,420
Let them in.

646
00:40:32,660 --> 00:40:34,190
Pleased to meet you, Mr. Ye.

647
00:40:35,360 --> 00:40:38,080
Or perhaps I should call you by your real name,

648
00:40:38,300 --> 00:40:39,250
Chen Ke.

649
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,030
Well...

650
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:45,240
Let me introduce myself.

651
00:40:45,880 --> 00:40:47,630
I am Shen Congwu,

652
00:40:48,070 --> 00:40:50,270
a secretary to the Director at NBIS.

653
00:40:50,390 --> 00:40:51,760
I have also read

654
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:53,170
your early works.

655
00:40:53,560 --> 00:40:55,360
They were truly extraordinary.

656
00:40:55,740 --> 00:40:57,030
If I had been

657
00:40:57,080 --> 00:40:59,080
a 17 or 18-year-old student back then,

658
00:40:59,080 --> 00:41:00,360
I might have been influenced by you as well.

659
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:03,090
The pursuit of truth is inherent to human nature.

660
00:41:04,250 --> 00:41:05,740
But for those like you

661
00:41:07,150 --> 00:41:09,050
who are full of lies,

662
00:41:09,270 --> 00:41:10,650
it's naturally incomprehensible.

663
00:41:10,650 --> 00:41:11,490
Truth

664
00:41:12,400 --> 00:41:14,080
is written by the victors.

665
00:41:14,700 --> 00:41:17,250
Now, the Japanese have surrendered.

666
00:41:17,510 --> 00:41:18,700
The Kuomintang-Communist peace talks

667
00:41:18,700 --> 00:41:20,030
merely provide your party with an opportunity

668
00:41:20,030 --> 00:41:21,400
to make a statement.

669
00:41:22,350 --> 00:41:24,480
If your party remains obstinate,

670
00:41:25,290 --> 00:41:27,420
it will face inevitable destruction.

671
00:41:27,450 --> 00:41:28,770
Mr. Chen, you must

672
00:41:29,020 --> 00:41:31,940
understand this situation.

673
00:41:33,630 --> 00:41:35,230
What I see

674
00:41:37,170 --> 00:41:39,130
before me is a group

675
00:41:40,150 --> 00:41:42,030
of strutting clowns.

676
00:41:48,090 --> 00:41:50,670
Let me explain my purpose today.

677
00:41:50,860 --> 00:41:51,740
Mr. Chen,

678
00:41:51,940 --> 00:41:53,800
Kuomintang respects people

679
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:57,720
of insight like you.

680
00:41:59,010 --> 00:42:01,470
If you can change your allegiance,

681
00:42:01,680 --> 00:42:02,580
I assure you

682
00:42:02,720 --> 00:42:05,650
that the generalissimo will hold you in high regard.

683
00:42:05,890 --> 00:42:07,380
Of course, I understand

684
00:42:07,600 --> 00:42:08,800
that someone like you

685
00:42:08,980 --> 00:42:11,380
is prepared to sacrifice for your beliefs.

686
00:42:12,770 --> 00:42:14,830
But after a life of military struggle

687
00:42:15,190 --> 00:42:16,590
and enduring hardships,

688
00:42:18,080 --> 00:42:19,430
you may not even

689
00:42:19,990 --> 00:42:21,670
live to see

690
00:42:21,710 --> 00:42:24,510
your so-called belief shine and prosper.

691
00:42:24,550 --> 00:42:25,580
Why bother?

692
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:28,580
Do you know what belief is?

693
00:42:29,070 --> 00:42:30,590
Do you understand belief?

694
00:42:30,760 --> 00:42:32,240
Do you have belief?

695
00:42:33,240 --> 00:42:35,760
It’s because of people like you,

696
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:40,120
who exploit the nation's suffering to line your pockets,

697
00:42:41,300 --> 00:42:42,540
ignoring the clamor

698
00:42:43,620 --> 00:42:45,120
of war

699
00:42:45,430 --> 00:42:47,280
and the people's plight,

700
00:42:47,600 --> 00:42:49,720
while hypocritically claiming

701
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:52,230
to serve the country and the people,

702
00:42:53,280 --> 00:42:55,200
that makes you despicable.

703
00:42:58,550 --> 00:43:01,210
The Kuomintang-Communist talks are imminent.

704
00:43:01,600 --> 00:43:02,520
Yet

705
00:43:03,550 --> 00:43:06,030
you have secretly detained me here.

706
00:43:07,800 --> 00:43:09,080
Listen well.

707
00:43:09,580 --> 00:43:10,660
We have long

708
00:43:11,270 --> 00:43:13,470
been prepared to sacrifice.

709
00:43:15,240 --> 00:43:17,630
Though the war against Japan is won,

710
00:43:18,670 --> 00:43:21,190
the fight isn’t over.

711
00:43:23,500 --> 00:43:25,610
As long as people like you are alive

712
00:43:26,000 --> 00:43:27,160
and standing there

713
00:43:28,240 --> 00:43:29,430
armed,

714
00:43:30,470 --> 00:43:31,560
we will

715
00:43:33,240 --> 00:43:34,560
continue to fight

716
00:43:35,600 --> 00:43:37,400
against you.

717
00:43:37,760 --> 00:43:39,370
I respect your choice.

718
00:43:40,590 --> 00:43:42,030
But I must tell you

719
00:43:42,190 --> 00:43:43,910
that you and your party

720
00:43:43,930 --> 00:43:46,250
only have a few days to consider.

721
00:43:48,070 --> 00:43:49,550
I hope to hear soon

722
00:43:50,150 --> 00:43:51,910
that you have abandoned your party

723
00:43:51,910 --> 00:43:53,170
and chosen

724
00:43:53,670 --> 00:43:54,910
a brighter path.
